Incubation
===

Masters experiment, incubation of soils amended with various amendments

Repository of walkthroughs for exploring 16s gene abundance data from soils

Prepare phyloseq object

## Load packages

```{r, cache=TRUE, warning=FALSE, message=FALSE}
library(phyloseq)
library(tidyverse)
```

## Read in the data 
use `readRDS` to load phyloseq object
```{r, cache=TRUE}
inc.raw <- readRDS("Data/incubation_raw.RDS")
inc.raw
```
